divs: Sighting DetailsWent out to smoke a cig and witnessed what looked like a star moving across the sky. I thought maybe it was a plane at first but this was not blinking. I called my friend and made him go outside and he was seeing what I was seeing. He recently saw possibly the same object on saint Patrick's day at a local bar we frequently visit. He has that sighting on tape
Summary: Star like moving across the sky from spnorth to south did not blink like plane was solid
